SAFA has today confirmed the dates of the 2016/2017 season s edition of the SAB league Provincial Play Offs that will commence from June 20th till June 17th. Teams will scribble for a spot in next season s ABC Motsepe League.The current second division and overall third tier of South African football features 144 teams in total, divided into 9 divisions located within the 9 provinces of South Africa .The champion of each provincial division qualifies for the annual Promotional Play-offs where they are divided into two streams with the winners of the two streams being promoted to the National First Division.Below are the confirmed play offs dates:&nbsp;-TNA Reporter 